c function is advisable.', 'Synergism', 'The use of naltrexone with other potentially hepatotoxic agents should be avoided whenever possible (e.', 'Moderate', 'pharmacodynamic', NULL, 'https://ddinter2.scbdd.com/server/interact/18362/', '', 'Codeine, Oliceridine, Oxymorphone, Naloxone, Tapentadol, Butorphanol, Dezocine, Opium, Dextropropoxyphene, Pentazocine, Dihydrocodeine, More', 'Glipizide, Acetohexamide, Guar gum, Pramlintide, Alogliptin, Tolazamide, Empagliflozin, Dulaglutide, Exenatide, Tolbutamide, Miglitol, More', 1767369485);
